Ian Mahinmi - Points

Ian Mahinmi scores a career high 32 points (2007)

On December 21, 2007, Ian Mahinmi tied his career high in points in a G-League game. That day he scored 32 points in Austin Spurs's road loss against Utah Flash, 118-116. He also had 17 rebounds, 2 assists, 5 steals and 3 blocks. He shot 11/15 from two, shooting at 73.3% from the field. He also shot 10/16 from the free-throw line.

Ian Mahinmi - Rebounds

Ian Mahinmi grabs a career high 17 rebounds (2007)

On December 21, 2007, Ian Mahinmi set his career high in rebounds in a G-League game. That day he grabbed 17 rebounds in Austin Spurs's road loss against Utah Flash, 118-116. He also had 32 points, 2 assists, 5 steals and 3 blocks.

Ian Mahinmi - Assists

Ian Mahinmi gives a career high 7 assists (2020)

On January 12, 2020, Ian Mahinmi set his career high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 7 assists in Washington's home loss against Utah, 116-127. He also had 15 points, 6 rebounds, 2 steals and 1 block.

Ian Mahinmi - Steals

Ian Mahinmi has a career high 7 steals (2017)

On March 07, 2017, Ian Mahinmi set his career high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 7 steals in Washington's road win against Phoenix, 127-131. He also had 15 points, 9 rebounds and 1 assist.

Ian Mahinmi - Blocks

Ian Mahinmi blocks a career high 7 shots (2008)

On February 23, 2008, Ian Mahinmi set his career high in blocks in a G-League game. That day he went for 7 blocks in Austin Spurs's home win against Santa Cruz Warriors, 118-87. He also had 30 points, 15 rebounds and 3 assists.

Ian Mahinmi - Efficiency

Ian Mahinmi records a career high 49 efficiency rating (2008)

On February 23, 2008, Ian Mahinmi set his career high in efficiency in a G-League game. That day he accomplished 49 efficiency in Austin Spurs's home win against Santa Cruz Warriors, 118-87. He also had 30 points, 15 rebounds and 3 assists.
